<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākābdē ratnatarkkadyumaṇisugaṇitē kā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>rttikē kṛṣṇapakṣē saptammyāṁ kavyavārē haritakula
<lb n="3" break="no"/>bhavaściṁgusēnādhināthaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> siṁhyādrīśasya hētōḥ
<lb n="4"/>śiśirakararucaśrīnṛsiṁhasya nityaṁ prādāmmālā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṁ guṇāḍyō dhanavibha<supplied reason="omitted">va</supplied>yaśasvāyurārōgyasi
<lb n="6" break="no"/>dyai <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śakavarṣaṁbulu 1269 gunēṇṭi kārttika kṛṣṇa sa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ptami śukravāramuna karṇadharakoṭṭara ciṁgusēnāpa
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ti tanaku Āyurārōgyaiśvaryyābhivṛ<unclear>dhi</unclear>gā ciṁgunā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>yaka gōpināthucēta mā 4ṇṭiki tōṁṭavilici Ītani cē<unclear>ta</unclear>
<lb n="10"/>mā 8 ṇṭiki kuṁcaprasādamu <unclear>ṭhāvupa</unclear>ṭṭe Ī prasādamu
<lb n="11"/><unclear>nitya</unclear> kuḍici vīriki puṇyamuga śrīnarasiṁhu<unclear>ni</unclear>
<lb n="12"/>nityamunnu tirumāla peṭaṁ [galāṁḍu I
<lb n="13"/>dharmmu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śrīśrīśrī]
</p>

